- Start-up contest for gender mainstreaming in RAC sector conducted: equipment for servicing refrigeration and air conditioning equipment was handed over to four winners start-up businesses of women; project will support further to ensure sustainability of the start-ups and higher job placement rate for women in RAC sector related business

